WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.410
Shu paytgacha biz "Android Framework" dagi 
"AudioManager" sinfi orqali 

00:00:03.410 --> 00:00:06.880
audio tinglashimiz kerak bo‘lganda 
audio fokusni talab qilishimizga 

00:00:06.880 --> 00:00:07.840
imkon berishini bilib oldik.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:13.100
Va so‘ngra audio fokusdan keyin ham 
voz kechishimizga imkon berdi.

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:15.640
Shuningdek, audio fokus holati 
o‘zgarganda xabardor bo‘lish uchun 

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:18.040
tinglovchilarni ro‘yxatdan 
o‘tkazishimiz mumkin.

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:21.120
Endi bu "Focus" ni boshqarishimiz uchun 
faoliyatimiz uchun "AudioManager" ob’ekti 

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:24.910
namunasiga muhtoj ekanligimizni anglatadi.

00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:29.720
Agar biz ushbu audio fokus darsligini, 
"Audio Focusni boshqarish" deb nomlangan 

00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:33.365
qismni ko‘rib chiqsak, unda biz ushbu 
kod satridan foydalanishimiz mumkinligi aytiladi.

00:00:33.365 --> 00:00:39.120
Bunga "AUDIO_SERVICE" ga kirish bilan 
"Context.getSystemService" olinadi.

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:42.360
"Audio Manager" sinfining 
namunasini olish uchun

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:46.360
Endi ushbu kod satridan "Audio Manager" tizim xizmati 
ekanligini ko‘ramiz.

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:48.940
Tizim xizmatlari haqida 
birinchi marta eshitishimiz.

00:00:48.940 --> 00:00:51.800
Shunday qilib, barcha funksiyalarni 
umumiy funksiyalar bilan ta’minlaydigan 

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:52.890
tizim xizmatlari mavjud, ya’ni 

00:00:52.890 --> 00:00:56.600
bildirishnoma yoki signalni boshqarish 
xizmati kabi narsalar.

00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:59.320
Qurilmada joylashuvni boshqarish xizmati kabi 
qo‘shimcha qurilmalarga kirishga imkon beradigan 

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:03.300
ba’zi xizmatlar ham mavjud.

00:01:03.300 --> 00:01:07.180
Ammo kunning oxirida tizim xizmati shunchaki 
"Java" sinfidir va u bilan ob’ekt namunasiga ega bo‘lib,

00:01:07.180 --> 00:01:10.540
undan foydalangan holda usullarni chaqirish 
orqali o‘zaro ishlashingiz mumkin.

